<SYNC Start=2329549><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2331254><P Class=KRCC>
죄송합니다
<SYNC Start=2332626><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2334890><P Class=KRCC>
서로 닮은 남매네요
<SYNC Start=2336428><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2337724><P Class=KRCC>
네?
<SYNC Start=2338364><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2338764><P Class=KRCC>
마샤야 군은<br>
